# Implementation Plan

## Dispatch Pattern

```bash
# Worker
claude -p "$(cat docs/plan/units/<unit>.md)" \
  --json-schema "$(cat docs/plan/schemas/worker-output.json)" \
  --output-format json --model opus --worktree \
  --dangerously-skip-permissions \
  --append-system-prompt "You are a worker agent. Implement exactly what the spec says. Do not ask questions."

# Verifier
claude -p "$(cat docs/plan/units/<unit>.md)" \
  --json-schema "$(cat docs/plan/schemas/verifier-output.json)" \
  --output-format json --model sonnet \
  --dangerously-skip-permissions \
  --append-system-prompt "You are a verifier agent. Run the checks specified. Report results only."

# Finalizer
claude -p "<commit instructions>" \
  --json-schema "$(cat docs/plan/schemas/finalizer-output.json)" \
  --output-format json --model sonnet \
  --dangerously-skip-permissions \
  --append-system-prompt "You are a finalizer agent. Commit and merge only. Do not modify code."
```

## Human-in-the-Loop Gates

| Gate | When | Action |
|------|------|--------|
| G1 | Plan 승인 | 이 문서 검토 후 진행 |
| G2 | Verify 실패 | 재시도 / 스펙 수정 / Unit 재분해 |
| G3 | Finalizer 전 | 병합 승인 |
| G4 | Plan 변경 | TOC 재구성 시 승인 |

